Name: You Doesn't Exist
About the game: Set out on an adventure that challenges all the codes of the RPG genre, toying with its boundaries to create something unlike anything you've ever seen. In a world full of magic and adventure, a young boy starts his apprenticeship to become a knight, protector of the Kingdom. He will face many challenges along the way, but overcoming them will allow him to grow into the hero the world needs. Join him in his quest to find himself, as his steps guide him towards something way bigger than him: the mystery surrounding the very nature of mankind and the fabric of reality itself. If you can get past the admittedly quirky open source game engine, you're in for a life changing experience.
